00:55:44.000 --> 00:55:49.000
 And then it would just add more or less glucose to reach the same potency.

00:55:49.000 --> 00:55:56.000
 But the new company decided to market calcitonin, extracting it from the material.

00:55:56.000 --> 00:56:04.000
 So now they kept selling it as Armour thyroid, but it was Armour thyroid minus thyrocalcitonin.

00:56:04.000 --> 00:56:09.000
 And then they started adding different binders.

00:56:09.000 --> 00:56:14.000
 At one point, they were using a polymer. I think they called it Explotab.

00:56:14.000 --> 00:56:19.000
 It was supposed to make the tablet dissolve instantly when it hit water.

00:56:19.000 --> 00:56:29.000
 And that was how the FDA had them demonstrate that in the presence of water, the polymer would basically puff up and release the glandular material immediately.

00:56:29.000 --> 00:56:36.000
